<%= render :partial => "/shared/error_and_notice" %>
<div style="width:800px;">
    <div class="title_large_red" >
		Thank you for adding <%=@saved_org.name%> to the Escent Community.
    </div>
	
	 <div class="title_red_nobold" >
		<br/><br/> 
		You, <strong><%= @current_user.full_name%></strong>, are assigned as the <strong>Administrator</strong> for <strong><%=@saved_org.name %>.</strong><br/><br/>
		From <%= @saved_org.name%>'s Network Page, you can access Administrator functions in order to:<br/><br/>
		 -  Update the organization's profile information and appearance preferences.<br/><br/>
		 -  Assign "Friends" of the organization to have various Authorizations, such as "Content Managers" or additional "Administrators".<br/><br/>
		 -  You can define roles (such as "Teacher") that your organization makes use of, and assign "Friends" to them.<br/><br/>
		 -  You can contribute material and manage <%=@saved_org.name%>'s contributions to the <strong>Resource Library</strong>.<br/><br/>
		 -  You can create/maintain <strong>Classrooms</strong>, and <strong>Blogs</strong> that your organziation may wish to have.<br/><br/>
		<br/><br/>
		As an Administrator, you are considered <%=@saved_org.name%>'s contact person for any service related issues.<br/><br/>   
		<strong><%= @saved_org.contact_name%></strong>, <%=@saved_org.contact_role%>, is considered to be <%=@saved_org.name%>'s management contact for all policy and business related issues.<br/>
		<br/><br/><br/>
		
		 
	<div style="color:#c73914;">
		<strong><p>Click on <%= link_to @saved_org.name, {:controller => "/site/site", :action => :static_organization, :organization_id => @saved_org} %> and setup your place in the comunity.</p></strong> 	<br/>	
	</div>
	
    </div>
	
    <div class="normal" style="margin-top:10px;">
        <strong>Please Note:</strong><br/>
		<strong>"Friends"</strong> are those Members who have registered from a page owned by your organization, or who have added <%= @saved_org.name %> to their favorites list.<br/>
    <br/><br/><br/></div>
	
	<div class="title_large_red" >
		Thank you again for joining the Escent Community!
    </div>
	
</div>
